description: This Dart file defines a Flutter widget representing the 'Feedback Center' screen for a manager within a mobile app. It includes UI components such as app bar, header, and placeholder items for feedback list, rating filter, and reply actions.

classes.name: ManagerFeedbackCenterScreen
classes.description: A stateless widget representing the manager's feedback center screen with a scaffold layout including a header and placeholder feedback items.

classes.name: _Item
classes.description: A stateless widget representing individual feedback or placeholder item with icon and text.

methods.name: build
methods.description: Builds the widget tree for the ManagerFeedbackCenterScreen, including app bar, header, and list of feedback items.

methods.name: _Item.build
methods.description: Builds the widget for an individual feedback or placeholder item with styling and icon.
